<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَالغُسْلُ لَهَا أَفْضَلُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَكُرِهَ نَومُ جُنُبٍ بِلَا وُضُوءٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> يَصِحُّ التَّيَمُّمُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> بِتُرَابٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> طَهُورٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> مُبَاحٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> لَهُ غُبَارٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> إِذَا عَدِمَ المَاءَ لِحَبْسٍ أَوْ غَيْرِهِ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ خِيفَ بِاسْتِعْمَالِهِ أَوْ طَلَبِهِ:</span> ضَرَرٌ بِبَدَنٍ، أَوْ مَالٍ، أَوْ غَيْرِهِمَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَيُفْعَلُ عَنْ كُلِّ مَا يُفْعَلُ بِالمَاءِ، سِوَى نَجَاسَةٍ عَلَى غَيْرِ بَدَنٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> إِذَا دَخَلَ وَقْتُ فَرْضٍ، وَأُبِيحَ غَيْرُهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَإِنْ وَجَدَ مَاءً لَا يَكْفِي طَهَارَتَهُ:</span> اسْتَعْمَلَهُ ثُمَّ تَيَمَّمَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>